FBIS4-63323 "drsov099_d_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 Regional Affairs Archangelsk Oblast Forms Own Government Archangelsk Oblast Forms Own Government LD2005140494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0900 GMT 20 May 94 LD2005140494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] Archangelsk Oblast has formed its own government. Pavel Balakshin, head of the oblast administration, appointed Valentin Vlasov, 48, to be its chairman. Up to now, Vlasov has been mayor of Archangelsk. Valentin Vlasov considers the establishment of a government is not merely another change of labels, but an attempt to set up an effective executive body which matches up to contemporary requirements.
